{"type": "article", "id": 29234, "title": "抹茶制品包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-06T22:51:56Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160706233355VakQTnMAGL96KtXw.png", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>RAWCHA 是一个来自巴西的抹茶品牌，<a href=\"http://sweetyand.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sweety &amp; Co.</a> 的设计师们在制品包装中采用了四种明亮的颜色与白色搭配排版，印上了各种原料和茶杯的小巧紧凑的图案，看上去轻快活泼。Sweety &amp; Co. 希望用这种风格与当地同类产品形成差异，用富有时尚感的基调吸引顾客。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234834Te2DBIRcwi56OGj9.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.250000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234835UH9uMGESBNXc3Imz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234837wGeEBtIvrcpTsoNJ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607062348373SwUbF5vWfxXO09a.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.574000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}